          "content": "We are reducing inequalities and improving outcomes for those living with cancer.",
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618218630053-07b524185bbf",
          "linkText": "EXPLORE OUR RESEARCH IN HEALTH INEQULITIES",
          "link": "#"
        },
